    public class SimpleInsert
extends java.lang.Object
implements Load
    Implement the initial database population according to the TPC-C database population requirements in Clause 4.3 using simple Insert sql statements

      • setSeed

        public void setSeed(long seed)
        Description copied from interface: Load
        Set the seed for the random number generator used to populate the data. Useful for testing to ensure consistent repeatable runs. If not set, defaults a value based upon current time. Must be called before setupLoad to have an effect.
        Specified by:
        setSeed in interface Load
